it.softphone.rd.model.shared
Interface Feed

public interface Feed

This interface represent a social feed, and cosumes the following json string: 

 { 
        'id':1,
        'issueId':1,
        'requestorId':'userId',
        'date':1341928641045,
        'action':'COMMENT',
        'text':'my message'
 }
An interface used by the following classes:
  • SocialBox
  • CommentBox
  • CommentBoxList
  • FeedBox

Author:
Alessandro Casolla
